ATTENTION BUYERS!!!!! SELLER IS OFFERING UP TO $5,000 IN CLOSING COSTS!!!!! Stunning 4-Bedroom, 3-Bath with Open Floorplan and Elegant Features Located in The Reserve at Pea Ridge. This immaculate 4-bedroom, 3-bath residence is a true gem, boasting a spacious open floorplan that exudes warmth and sophistication. Situated in a desirable neighborhood, this home offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and functionality.

The 4 well-appointed bedrooms offer ample space and comfort, making it easy to unwind and relax with plush carpet in all bedrooms. The master suite is a true sanctuary, complete with an ensuite bathroom that includes a double vanity and walk-in closet. The additional 2 bathrooms are tastefully designed and conveniently located for family and guests.
The rest of the home is tiled throughout with a modern kitchen design with granite countertops and a large island that opens to the breakfast and living area. 
Right off the living and breakfast area is the covered, extended back porch with a charming pergola and storage shed that will convey with the home. 
Located in a sought-after neighborhood, this home is close to schools, parks, shopping, and dining options. It offers easy access to major highways for a stress-free commute. Don't miss your opportunity to own this exceptional 4-bedroom, 3-bath home with an open floorplan, elegant kitchen, and a delightful outdoor retreat. Schedule a showing today and discover the lifestyle this home can offer you and your family!
